metadata.title: Bald Eagle Hydrocarbon Exposure

creators.name: Wildlife Service (USFWS), Oil Spill Administration Office

metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  This theme documents samples taken to determine exposure to hydrocarbons. Data includes sample location (lat/long), type of sample (egg shell, egg contents, blood, feather, etc.), and exposure (yes or no). Scale is 1:63,360.
